 {"title": "RevOps Building a Forecasting Process from Scratch", "description": "A RevOps leader at a Series D company replacing spreadsheet forecasting implements Clari across a 120-person sales org. Phase one (weeks 1-4) connects Clari to Salesforce, Gmail, and Gong. Phase two (weeks 5-8) configures forecast categories, pipeline stages, and deal scoring weights. Phase three (months 3-6) trains the team on Clari's interface and compares AI forecasts against manual submissions. By month 6, the AI forecast is consistently within 7% of actuals while manual submissions average 18% variance. The company standardizes on Clari's number for all planning."},
