 {"question": "How long does Clari implementation take?", "answer": "Standard implementation takes 4-8 weeks for CRM connection, data sync, and basic configuration. Full deployment with custom forecast categories, trained AI models, and organizational adoption takes 3-6 months. The AI models need at least 2 quarters of historical data to produce accurate forecasts. Plan for a dedicated RevOps resource spending 10-15 hours per week during the first month."},
